<para style="q1">

<verse number="27" style="v" />I also will place him as my firstborn son,</para>

<para style="q1">the most exalted of the kings of the earth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="28" style="v" />I will extend my covenant faithfulness to him forever;</para>

<para style="q1">and my covenant with him will be secure.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="29" style="v" />I will make his descendants endure forever</para>

<para style="q1">and his throne as enduring as the skies above.</para>
